stories.title: All about discipline
stories.subTitle: Australia v New Zealand, TVS Cup, Game 7, Guwahati
stories.summary: Daryl Tuffey and Kyle Mills took four important wickets but left a lot to be desired with their consistency

stories.title: Problems at the top
stories.subTitle: Australia v New Zealand, TVS Cup, Game 7, Guwahati
stories.summary: Even before the tournament, New Zealand's battingwould have been ranked third of the three at the TVSCup, but when the first two positions are occupied byAustralia and India - in whichever order - that is nocriticism
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Samanth Subramanian

stories.title: Bevan inspires Australia to victory
stories.subTitle: Australia v New Zealand, TVS Cup, Game 7, Guwahati
stories.summary: Australia thrashed New Zealand in a low-scoring match after losing the toss - and their top order - early in the game, underlining just what a great side they are
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by S Rajesh
